### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### UPDATE
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [3.1] Sửa ngân sách: đổi amount + đổi category
PUT http://localhost:9999/api/budgets/{{budget_id_1}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 4000000,
  "beginDate": "2026-03-01",
  "endDate": "2026-03-31",
  "walletId": null,
  "allCategories": false,
  "categoryId": 5,
  "repeating": true
}

###

### [3.2] Sửa sang allCategories=true (xóa hết categories cũ)
PUT http://localhost:9999/api/budgets/{{budget_id_1}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000000,
  "beginDate": "2026-03-01",
  "endDate": "2026-03-31",
  "walletId": null,
  "allCategories": true,
  "categoryId": null,
  "repeating": false
}

###

